data.description: If you're looking for space, you've found it! This large family home will provide you with plenty of room to spread out and relax, especially in the sauna.  There's lots of storage too, with several walk-in closets, loads of kitchen cabinets & convenient mudroom/laundry room storage space as well.  Both the main floor bedroom & the basement level bedroom have extra-large ensuite bathrooms & massive walk-in closets.  There is also a 16x28 deck off of the informal dining area to grill and enjoy the sunset on.  You'll be looking over your tree-lined backyard, providing plenty of privacy on your 3+acre lot. Got toys? Did I mention the 3 car garage? Your family and pets will be safe should you decide to utilize the ADT System and invisible fencing that are in place.  Recent updates include: new 50 gallon water heater - 12/21, new pressure tank, pressure switch, gauge, capacitor, and main shut off - 7/21, new roof - 5/18, invisible fence - 5/17, and all new windows on the main level - 6/17.
